==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Memorial rose
<hw>Memorial rose</hw>. <def>A Japanese evergreen rose (<spn>Rosa
wichuraiana</spn>) with creeping branches, shining leaves, and single
white flowers. It is often planted in cemeteries.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Memorist</ent>⟦br⟧
